data.description: **$7500 buyer incentive for closing costs or buyer's choice.**Stunning Property! Move-In Ready with No Wait Time or High HOA Expenses!This property shows like a new construction without the wait for completion & price tag! The open concept living room looks into the beautiful kitchen with plenty of cabinet/granite counter space, Stainless Steel appliances, stunning light fixtures & boasts an eat in area with separate formal dining. The 2nd floor has a walk in laundry room, additional full bath & 4 spacious bedrooms including the primary with a wonderful ensuite bathroom equipped with a dual vanity, soaker tub, stand up shower & huge walk in closet. Expansive third floor, features a spacious bonus room with a private full bath. Whether you need an additional bedroom, office or game room, this flexible space can accommodate all your needs. The fully fenced yard offers ample privacy and plenty of space for entertaining or for your fur babies to run & play. This home is located minutes away from schools, shopping, dining & Fort Liberty.
